{
  "id": "adv_main_02_08_01",
  "title": "東京編2章11話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tension-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "トーナメントのシード枠は各事務所につき一枠までか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ each agency is only allowed one seeded group.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_01-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "けど、冷静に考えればそうよね\nシード枠が多くても、意味ないし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But‚ when you think about it‚ it actually makes sense.\nIt wouldn’t make sense to have too many seeded groups.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_01-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "むしろ、事務所毎に一枠って制約は\n公平を期す意味でも妥当ね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If anything‚ having one seeded group per agency\nis a valid way of promoting fairness.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.166666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_01-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "でも、シード枠に入れなかったグループは\nどうなっちゃうんだろう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But what about the groups that aren’t seeded?\nWhat happens to them?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.8333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_01-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "通常枠でエントリーして、勝ち上がるしかないわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Their only choice is to enter normally and win their way to the top.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.766666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_01-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "問題は、どのグループがシード枠で出るか、だね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I guess the issue here is which group gets to be seeded.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_01-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "それはもちろん！\n月のテンペストで決まりですわ！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But of course!\nThat would have to be Moon Tempest!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_moon-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 35.63333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_01-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "すずにゃん、声でっか！\nいきなりどうしたの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Suzu-nyan‚ you’re too loud!\nWhat are you screaming about?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_01-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "失礼、つい勢いづいてしまいましたわ\nですがそのシード権、他に選択肢などないでしょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Pardon‚ I got a little over-excited.\nBut if you wish to choose a seeded group‚ there’s no other option.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_01-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "星見プロの看板を背負って立つんですから\n私達月ストが一番ふさわしいのは明らかですわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "To carry the banner of Hoshimi Productions to the top‚\nwe‚ Moon Tempest‚ are clearly the best choice!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.333333333333336,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_01-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "うーん、すずにゃんさすがですね！\nさっきまでのビクビクおどおどアタフタが嘘みたいです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah-hah. Well said‚ Suzu-nyan!\nIt’s hard to believe she was the same cowardly‚ sniveling girl from before!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.3333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_01-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "すずにゃんはいつもそんな感じだよ？\nそういう所が放っておけなくて可愛いんだよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Suzu-nyan’s always like that‚ though.\nThat’s what makes her so adorable you just want to take care of her.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.74870990953947,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_01-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "そこ！　茶化さないでくださる！？\n私は本気も本気ですのよ！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey! Quit making fun of me!\nI am seriously serious‚ you know?!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_01-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "すずの意気込みには共感出来るわね\nでも……シード枠にふさわしいのはサニピよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I can sympathize with Suzu’s enthusiasm.\nBut… if you want to know who deserves to be the seeded group‚ it’s Sunny Peace.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_sun-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 84.06666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_01-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "で、でも、もっとランキング上位のグループとか\n沢山出るんだよね？　私達で、勝てるのかな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "B-but… wouldn’t lots of higher-ranking groups\ncompete against us? Would we really be able to beat them?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_01-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "やる前から弱気にならないの\n不安な所はとことんサポートするから、頑張るわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don’t lose your nerve before the fight.\nI’ll have your back in the parts where you feel shaky. We can do this.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_01-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "千紗はちゃんと、ダンスも歌もうまくなっている\nだから、もっと自信を持って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’ve gotten a lot better at singing and dancing‚ Chisa.\nSo believe in yourself.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_01-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "れ、怜ちゃんにそう言われると\nなんだか凄く照れちゃうね……えへへ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "R-Rei-chan‚ hearing that from you…\nit kind of makes me really embarrassed. Hahaha.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_01-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "でも、そうだよね\nみんなと一緒なら私、頑張れると思う……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But… you’re right.\nAs long as I’m with all you girls‚ I think I can do it!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_01-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "ふふっ、千紗がやる気になっているなら\nお姉ちゃんだって負けてられないわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe. Well‚ if you’re up for the challenge‚ Chisa‚\nas you older sister‚ I’ll have to step up as well.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_liz-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 135.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_01-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "みんな、モチベーション上がってるみたいね\nただ、私達を忘れてもらったら困るわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It sounds like you’re all really motivated.\nBut we can’t let you forget about us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_01-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "まあ正直、僕はどこがシード枠でもいいと思うけど\n莉央がこだわってるなら、狙ってみてもいいかもね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ to be honest‚ I don’t really care who the seeded group is.\nBut if you want it‚ Rio‚ I don’t mind fighting for it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_01-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん、忘れてなんかいないよ\nただ、私達も譲れないってだけ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course we haven’t forgotten about you.\nIt’s just that we also don’t want to give it up so easily.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 149.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_01-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "ここにいるみんな、気持ちは同じです\n……でも、だからこそ選びきれないわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everyone here feels the same way.\nBut… I guess that’s why we can’t decide.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 156.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_01-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "三グループのうち、どこがシード権を得るのか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Which of us three groups should be the seeded group?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 160.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_01-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "ここはやはり、クジで決めましょうか？\nその方が、みんな公平ですし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Maybe we should decide by lottery?\nThat would be the fairest for everyone.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 167.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_01-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "え～？　せっかくだからもっと勝負っぽくしようよ～\n例えばモノマネ対決とか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What? Come on‚ this is a great opportunity for a competition!\nLike… an imitation contest?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 175.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_comical-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 175.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_08_01-kkr003.m4a",
      "text": "あ、それなら私、最近レパートリー増えたんですよ～\nにがーいコーヒーを飲んじゃったすずにゃんやりま～す",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ooh! I’ve recently expanded my repertoire.\nLet me do my impression of Suzu-nyan drinking bitter coffee!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 183.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
