      "text": "あはは！　二人はすっかり仲良しさんだなぁ……\nあの、{user}さんはどう思いますか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hahaha! You two are thick as thieves already.\nUm‚ what do you think‚ {user}-san?",
