      "text": "そうだな……確かに難しくて決められないよな\nでも、互いに実力を見せ合うってのはありだろう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let me see… I agree that it’s a hard decision to make.\nBut it would make sense to have some sort of talent competition.",
